  "text": "# FEES & CHARGES  \n**Q: Does FirstUK Bank charge hidden fees?**\nA: No. All fees are clearly shown in our Pricing Guide at www.firstuk.bank/pricing  \n**Q: What are the main fees?**\nA:\n- **Monthly Account Fee:** £0 (all products)\n- **International ATM:** £2.50 per withdrawal\n- **International Transfer:** £5.00\n- **Card Replacement:** £15.00 (expedited: £25.00)  \n**Q: Are there early repayment penalties (mortgages)?**\nA: Yes, for fixed-rate mortgages (1–3% of outstanding balance). Variable rates have no early repayment fee.  \n**Q: Will my fees change?**\nA: We may change fees with 30 days notice. You can close your account with no penalty if you disagree.  \n---",
